  "texts": [
    "Our main contributions are summarized as follows:",
    "Categorization and review.",
    "We present a detailed categorization and novel taxonomies of research on unifying LLMs and KGs.",
    "In each category, we review the research from the perspectives of different integration strategies and tasks, which provides more insights into each framework. 2.",
    "Coverage of emerging advancements."
  ]
